revision.text:
The '''1986 [[Lamar Hunt U.S. Open Cup|National Challenge Cup]]''' was the 72nd edition of the USSF's annual open soccer championship. Teams from the [[American Soccer League (1933-1983)|American Soccer League]] declined to participate.  <br>[[St. Louis Kutis S.C.|Kutis SC]] of St. Louis defeated San Pedro Yugoslavs 1-0 in the final game.<ref>{{cite web|title=1986 US Open Cup|url=http://thecup.us/1986-us-open-cup-results/|publisher=TheCup.us|accessdate=5 June 2011}}</ref> 

