{{use dmy dates|date=May 2016}} {{Infobox sportsperson | name = Gilbert Orengo | image = | caption = | birth_name = | fullname = | nationality = | residence = | birth_date = {{birth date and age|1934|3|10|df=yes}} | birth_place = [[Monaco]] | death_date = | death_place = | height = | weight = | website = | country = | sport = [[Fencing]] | event = | collegeteam = | club = | team = | turnedpro = | coach = | retired = | coaching = | worlds = | regionals = | nationals = | olympics = | paralympics = | highestranking = | pb = | show-medals = yes }} '''Gilbert Orengo''' (born 10 March 1934) is a [[Monaco|Monegasque]] [[fencing|fencer]]. He competed in the individual [[foil (fencing)|foil]] and [[épée]] events at the [[1960 Summer Olympics]].<ref name="sports-reference">{{cite web|url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/or/gilbert-orengo-1.html |title=Gilbert Orengo Olympic Results |accessdate=2010-11-02 |work=sports-reference.com |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110916181142/http://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/or/gilbert-orengo-1.html |archivedate=16 September 2011 |df=dmy }}</ref>
